{"tid":514127,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多個城市爆反政府示威","createTime":"2017-12-30T08:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T10:39:41.000Z","uid":28366,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e37e2f264dc17d395d4f04480d95921f3fdf0e5","tid":514127,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/165112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F165112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a49e320a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊朗全國多個城市連續兩天舉行反政府集會示威，抗議物價高漲以及不滿政府的經濟政策，警方拘捕數十人，引來美國譴責。<br />\n<br />\n在首都德黑蘭以及早前受地震重創的西部城市克爾曼沙阿(Kermanshah)周五都有示威者聚集，克爾曼沙阿大約有300人集會，高叫反政府口號「釋放政治犯」、「不自由毋寧死」，警方到場驅散，有多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n德黑蘭則大約有50人在公共廣場集會示威，抗議物價高漲，警方驅散集會並拘捕少數人。為了反制反政府示威，德黑蘭街頭後來聚集了4,000人撐政府，又指國家的經濟問題罪魁禍首是美國。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗至少有六個城市連續舉行反政府集會，相信是2009年以來最大規模，令總統魯哈尼(Hassan Rouhani)的政府受壓。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普讚揚民眾和平示威，對當局的貪腐表達不滿，又警告伊朗政府克制，「伊朗政府應尊重人民的權利，包括表達己見的權利。世界在看著！」<br />\n<br />\n第二大城市馬什哈德(Mashhad)等多個城市周四已爆發示威，社交網流傳的片段見到警方出動水炮及催淚彈鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171230/57643861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F57643861&d=K2ZWUtMstStDIes0vZ4PKmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=c5e24f2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F57643861&h=54ab7bd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171230/57643861</a>"},{"pid":"098852fa3091783355f62fa0383c3904767e7cde","tid":514127,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2e011b8807d7a321975cbe073193b1d674eb63","tid":514127,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c37ea4cb447b18ad86041c785a200f9ed9d910a","tid":514127,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"香港也時常爆發撐政府示威"},{"pid":"c2572dea7aff9c3322bbf6592c862b313f22ba2f","tid":514127,"uid":57604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"唔係話伊朗好open好nice <br />\n同綠色革命一樣<br />\n一定又係美國操控嘅主流媒體輿論抹黑伊朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f64688f4bdb4689ca55328f7b8bc03a5e0645d","tid":514127,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}